org.openbel.framework.common
Class SimpleOutput

java.lang.Object
  org.openbel.framework.common.SimpleOutput
All Implemented Interfaces:
Reportable
public final class SimpleOutput
extends Object
implements Reportable

Prints errors and warnings via direct hand-off to the underlying streams.

  1. Warnings will be printed with the line prefix WARNING: .
  2. Errors will be printed with the line prefix ERROR: .
